title: VA Indie Easy Rock NOV 2013 - Stay With Me (Dutch Treat I2)
description:
Like Number 5, music is very much alive. Already the first Indie Playlist of November 2013. A special list. Sometimes that happens. I have to warn you though for the last track. There is a warning outstanding. I would not play it in public (my first time, something is on the list, I would not love to play in public). But in a way its a very interesting peace of music.... Enjoy, 

PS: Thanks Jamal for Kiddo. She balanced painting the list (and everybody else, for the rest :)).
